Left%20and%20one%20from%20an%20ultra-Left%20organisation.%20There%20is%20a%20deep%20conspiracy%20against%20the%20government.%20They%20were%20talking%20about%20a%20plot.%20They%20will%20attack%20the%20%3Cem%3E'dharna'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sit-in)%20of%20doctors%20and%20then%20will%20blame%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20state%20government%20that%20after%20yesterday's%20deadlock%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20attacking%20the%20doctors...%20this%20is%20the%20main%20plot%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ghosh%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20made%20the%20same%20claim%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20and%20said%20the%20police%20should%20stop%20the%20entry%20of%20outsiders%20near%20the%20protest%20site%20at%20Swasthya%20Bhavan%2C%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20health%20department%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20in%20Kolkata's%20Salt%20Lake%2C%20where%20the%20doctors%20began%20a%20sit-in%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20on%20their%20own%20and%20also%20arrested%20one%20person.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECPI(M)%20spokesperson%20Fuad%20Halim%20said%20the%20police%20should%20investigate%20how%20Mr%20Ghosh%20got%20the%20clip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20August%2014%2C%20when%20a%20peaceful%20protest%20was%20on%2C%20a%20big%20group%20of%20goons%20entered%20RG%20Kar%20hospital%20and%20tried%20to%20compromise%20the%20scene%20of%20crime.%20The%20administration%20is%20totally%20silent%20on%20the%2020-30%20people%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%20-%20who%20they%20were%2C%20what%20are%20their%20political%20affiliations%2C%20why%20they%20went%20on%20a%20rampage.%20Devious%20forces%20are%20working%20here%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20Trinamool%20Congress%20is%20involved%20in%20a%20heinous%20threat%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Halim%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20moves%20for%20a%20discussion%20between%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20protesting%20doctors%20since%20Tuesday%2C%20which%20have%20been%20getting%20stalled.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20doctors%20had%20made%20four%20key%20demands%20for%20the%20discussion%20to%20take%20place%3A%20they%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20send%20a%20delegation%20of%20at%20least%2030%2C%20the%20discussion%20should%20be%20held%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20it%20should%20be%20centred%20around%20their%20five-point%20demands%2C%20and%20the%20meeting%20should%20be%20live%20telecast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20the%20four%20demands%20had%20been%20met%20and%20the%20doctors%20had%20reached%20the%20state%20secretariat%20on%20Thursday%20for%20a%20meeting%20but%20it%20did%20not%20take%20place%20because%20the%20government%20did%20not%20agree%20to%20a%20'live%20telecast'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Against%20Protocol'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20reasoning%20after%20Thursday's%20meeting%20did%20not%20happen%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20said%20she%20had%20been%20waiting%20for%20the%20doctors%20for%20over%20two%20hours%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20matter%20was%20in%20court%20and%20live%20streaming%20the%20meeting%20would%20be%20against%20protocol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20also%20apologised%20to%20the%20people%20of%20West%20Bengal%20and%20said%20she%20was%20willing%20to%20step%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20people%2C%20I%20am%20ready%20to%20step%20down.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20the%20post%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20I%20want%20justice%20for%20Tilottama%20(the%20name%20given%20to%20the%20trainee%20doctor%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered).%20And%20I%20want%20common%20people%20to%20get%20medical%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20people%20do%20not%20know%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20colour%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20protest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20many%20in%20the%20delegation%20we