undwater%20extraction.%20While%20some%20of%20the%20measures%20she%20has%20listed%20below%20are%20already%20being%20implemented%20to%20some%20extent%20thanks%20to%20the%20Union%20Government-sponsored%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353376%2Fabhijeet-gan-rite-water-solutions-million-litres-clean-drinking-water-jal-jeevan-mission-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJal%20Jeevan%20Mission%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20on%20war%20footing%20to%20ensure%20long-term%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Mandatory%20permits%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20All%20individuals%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20institutions%20should%20be%20required%20to%20obtain%20permits%20for%20drilling%20borewells%20and%20extracting%20groundwater.%20Permits%20should%20be%20granted%20based%20on%20a%20thorough%20assessment%20of%20the%20local%20groundwater%20resources%20and%20the%20sustainability%20of%20extraction.%20Authorities%2C%20including%20the%20Public%20Health%20and%20Engineering%20Department%2C%20must%20mandate%20a%20thorough%20site%20inspection%20before%20granting%20permissions%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20new%20borewells%20or%20septic%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Metering%20of%20groundwater%20usage%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20installation%20of%20water%20meters%20should%20be%20made%20compulsory%20for%20all%20groundwater%20extraction%20points.%20This%20will%20help%20monitor%20and%20regulate%20groundwater%20usage%2C%20ensuring%20that%20extraction%20remains%20within%20sustainable%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Pricing%20of%20groundwater%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Introduce%20a%20pricing%20mechanism%20for%20groundwater%20usage%20to%20discourage%20excessive%20extraction%20and%20promote%20conservation.%20This%20can%20be%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20groundwater%20tax%20or%20a%20tiered%20pricing%20system%20based%20on%20consumption%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Zoning%20regulations%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Implement%20strict%20zoning%20regulations%20to%20control%20the%20density%20of%20borewells%20and%20prevent%20over-extraction%20in%20critical%20groundwater%20recharge%20areas.%20This%20may%20involve%20establishing%20%E2%80%98no-go%E2%80%99%20zones%20where%20groundwater%20extraction%20is%20prohibited%20or%20restricted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Strict%20enforcement%20of%20waste%20disposal%20regulations%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EImplement%20stringent%20regulations%20on%20the%20disposal%20of%20solid%20waste%2C%20sewage%2C%20and%20industrial%20effluents%20to%20prevent%20contamination%20of%20groundwater.%20This%20should%20include%20mandatory%20treatment%20of%20waste%20before%20disposal%2C%20regular%20monitoring%20of%20disposal%20sites%2C%20and%20hefty%20fines%20for%20hotels%20and%20other%20businesses%20found%20dumping%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20including%20expired%20cement%20into%20water%20bodies.%20Moreover%2C%20clear%20guidelines%20must%20be%20set%20on%20the%20minimum%20distance%20that%20must%20be%20maintained%20between%20borewells%20and%20septic%20tanks%2C%20based%20on%20the%20local%20hydrogeological%20conditions%20and%20the%20potential%20risk%20of%20contamination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Launch%20a%20public%20awareness%20campaign%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20educate%20citizens%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20maintaining%20the%20proper%20distance%20between%20borewells%20and%20septic%20tanks%2C%20and%20the%20potential%20health%20risks%20associated%20with%20groundwater%20contamination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Install%20water-efficient%20fixtures%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Encourage%20hotels%2C%20guesthouses%2C%20and%20restaurants%20to%20install%20water-efficient%20fixtures%2C%20such%20as%20low-flow%20faucets%2C%20promote%20use%20of%20greywater%20recycling%20systems%2C%20and%20use%20treated%20water%20for%20non-potable%20purposes%20like%20irrigation%20and%20toilet%20flushing.%20They%20should%20also%20be%20mandated%20to%20undergo%20regular%20water%20audits%2C%20install%20rainwater%20harvesting%20systems%2C%20and%20receive%20financial%20incentives%20like%20tax%20cuts%20if%20they%20meet%20certain%20water%20conservation%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20convince%20the%20industry%20to%20invest%20urgently%2C%20we%20need%20to%20emphasise%20both%20the%20environmental%20necessity%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20cost%20savings%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357468%2Fias-officer-revive-water-table-cdo-varanasi-himanshu-nagpal-rainwater-harvesting-river-rejuvenation-groundwater-recharge%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eefficient%20water%20use%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Collaborating%20with%20eco-tourism%20certification%20programmes%20could%20provide%20an%20additional%20incentive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Regular%20monitoring%20and%20mapping%20of%20groundwater%20resources%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Establish%20a%20comprehensive%20groundwater%20monitoring%20network%20and%20regularly%20map%20the%20groundwater%20resources%20to%20assess%20the%20impact%20of%20extraction%20and%20inform%20regulatory%20decisions.%20This%20is%20a%20particularly%20important%20concern%20given%20the%20lack%20of%20concrete%20data%20on%20the%20scale%20of%20groundwater%20extraction%20in%20Leh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Groundwater-Dr-Chorol-1726237249.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Lobzang%20Chorol%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20six%20years%20studying%20Leh's%20groundwater.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Groundwater-Dr-Chorol-1726237249.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Gr