ial%20visit%20to%20Doda%20was%20in%201982%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Union%20Coal%20and%20Mines%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20election%20in-charge%20for%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20G%20Kishan%20Reddy%2C%20on%20Friday%20in%20Samba.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%C2%A0Modi's%20rally%20is%20all%20set%20to%20give%20boost%20to%20his%20cadres%20and%20candidates%20in%20the%20region%20where%20voting%20for%20eight%20Assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20three%20districts%20of%20the%20Chenab%20Valley%20%E2%80%94%20Doda%2C%20Kishtwar%2C%20and%20Ramban%20%E2%80%94%20is%20scheduled%20for%20September%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202014%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20PM%20Modi%20addressed%20a%20BJP%20poll%20rally%20in%20Kishtwar%20district.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Doda%20have%20been%20eagerly%20waiting%20to%20see%20and%20hear%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20a%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20believe%20that%20the%20prime%20minister's%20visit%20will%20significantly%20boost%20the%20electoral%20prospects%20of%20party%20candidates%20in%20the%20union%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20is%20contesting%20all%2043%20Assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20Jammu%20division.%20In%20the%20last%20J%26amp%3BK%20Assembly%2C%20BJP%20had%2025%20MLAs.%C2%A0%20Voting%20in%20the%20J-K%20Assembly%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20in%20three%20phases%20on%20September%2018%2C%20September%2025%2C%20and%20October%201.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20take%20place%20on%20October%208.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20Assembly%20election%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20in%2010%20years%2C%20and%20the%20first%20since%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Articles%20370%20and%2035A.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu%20region%20has%20long%20been%20a%20BJP%20stronghold%2C%20with%20the%20party%20winning%20all%2025%20of%20its%20seats%20from%20this%20region%20in%20the%202014%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20addressed%20