Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20widely%20known%20as%20'Captain%20Cool'%20for%20maintaining%20a%20calm%20demeanour%20even%20in%20adverse%20situations.%20This%20trait%20alongside%20his%20tactical%20acumen%20and%20self-belief%20has%20helped%20Dhoni%20become%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20leaders%20of%20all%20time.%20Notably%2C%20Dhoni%20is%20the%20only%20captain%20in%20cricket%20history%20to%20win%20all%20three%20major%20ICC%20white-ball%20trophies%20-%20T20%20World%20Cup%20(in%202007)%2C%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20(In%202011)%20and%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20(in%202013).%20Not%20only%20this%2C%20Dhoni%20led%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK)%20to%20a%20record%20equalling%20five%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20titles%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni's%20former%20India%20and%20ex-CSK%20teammate%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Subramaniam%20Badrinath%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F856-subramaniam-badrinath-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESubramaniam%20Badrinath%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20revealed%20an%20unheard%20tale%20of%20the%20legendary%20player.%20The%20incident%20that%20Badrinath%20narrated%20had%20the%20rare%20instance%20of%20Dhoni%20losing%20his%20cool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20also%20a%20human...he%20has%20lost%20his%20cool%2C%26quot%3B%20Badrinath%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insidesport.in%2Fcricket%2Fms-dhoni-was-not-always-captain-cool-reveals-ex-csk-teammate-s-badrinath%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInsideSport%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20that%20has%20never%20happened%20on%20the%20field.%20He%20would%20never%20let%20the%20opposition%20know%20that%20he%20had%20lost%20his%20cool.%20In%20this%20match%20against%20RCB%20in%20Chennai%2C%20we%20were%20chasing%20110%20odd.%20We%20lost%20wickets%20in%20a%20cluster%20there%20and%20we%20ended%20up%20losing%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20out%20to%20a%20lap%20shot%20against%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Anil%20Kumble%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F265-anil-kumble-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAnil%20Kumble%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20LBW.%20So%2C%20I%20was%20standing%20inside%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20and%20he%20was%20coming%20inside%2C%20where%20there%20was%20a%20small%20water%20bottle.%20MS%20just%20kicked%20it%20out%20of%20the%20park.%20We%20all%20just%20couldn't%20make%20eye%20contact%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Badrinath%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20IPL%20mega%20auction%20is%20just%20some%20months%20away%2C%20the%20uncertainty%20over%20Dhoni's%20future%20in%20the%20tournament%20is%20still%20uncertain.%20Amid%20the%20speculations%20of%20his%20retirement%2C%20the%20player%20has%20remained%20tight-lipped%20about%20the%20chances%20of%20his%20participation%20in%20IPL%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20a%20mega%20auction%20before%20the%20upcoming%20edition%20means%20that%20things%20are%20going%20to%20be%20tough%20for%20the%20CSK%20franchise%20if%20they%20opt%20to%20include%20Dhoni%20as%20a%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E43-year-old%20Dhoni%2C%20who%20called%20time%20on%20his%20international%20career%20in%20August%2C%202020%2C%20is%20close%20to%20his%20retirement%20from%20cricket.%20Hence%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20a%20right%20decision%20if%20CSK%20decide%20to%20retain%20him%20as%20it%20will%20fill%20one%20of%20the%20few%20slots%20that%20the%20franchise%20will%20be%20getting%20ahead%20of%20the%20auction.%20Meanwhile%2C%20CSK%20would%20also%20not%20want%20to%20exclude%20the%20legendary%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726279380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fm9it9f1_ms-dhoni_625x300_29_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fms-dhoni-lost-his-cool-kicked-water-bottle-out-of-the-park-ex-csk-star-reveals-