nald%20Trump%20specifically%20of%20wanting%20to%20privatize%20the%20VA%2C%20a%20charge%20Republicans%20have%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20presidential%20nominee%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris'%20campaign%20quickly%20seized%20on%20Vance's%20remarks%2C%20posting%20to%20social%20media%20a%20nine-second%20clip%20of%20Vance%20saying%20he%20would%20consider%20privatization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20just%20some%20misguided%20policy%20idea%3B%20it's%20a%20slap%20in%20the%20face%20to%20the%20men%20and%20women%20who%20served%20this%20country%2C%20coming%20from%20the%20man%20running%20alongside%20the%20candidate%20who%20called%20them%20'suckers'%20and%20'losers%2C'%26quot%3B%20Sen.%20Tammy%20Duckworth%2C%20a%20Democrat%20from%20Illinois%2C%20a%20Harris%20campaign%20cochair%20and%20Iraq%20War%20veteran%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20provided%20by%20the%20campaign.%20%26quot%3BVeterans%20deserve%20better%20than%20candidates%20who%20will%20turn%20their%20healthcare%20into%20a%20business%20opportunity%20the%20minute%20they%20get%20the%20chance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20campaign%20shot%20back%20that%20the%20Harris%20campaign%20was%20taking%20Vance%20out%20of%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20full%20exchange%2C%20Sen.%20Vance%20clearly%20says%20he%20would%20not%20privatize%20the%20Department%20of%20Veterans%20Affairs%2C%26quot%3B%20William%20Martin%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Vance%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FMilitary.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMilitary.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Kamala%20campaign%20is%20once%20again%20twisting%20his%20words%20and%20lying%20about%20his%20position%20because%20they%20have%20nothing%20but%20a%20record%20of%20abject%20failure%20to%20run%20on.%20It's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20JD%20personally%20relied%20on%20the%20VA%20for%20years%20after%20leaving%20the%20Marine%20Corps.%20They%20should%20be%20ashamed%20for%20intentionally%20lying%20about%20a%20veteran%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20providing%20quality%20care%20and%20coverage%20for%20our%20veterans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20first%20term%20in%20office%2C%20Trump%20expanded%20veterans'%20ability%20to%20see%20non-VA%20doctors%20using%20VA%20funding%20by%20signing%20the%20Mission%20Act.%20While%20veterans%20had%20already%20been%20able%20to%20seek%20outside%20health%20care%20following%20the%202014%20VA%20wait-time%20scandal%2C%20the%20Mission%20Act%20grew%20the%20number%20of%20veterans%20eligible%20for%20outside%20care%20and%20consolidated%20several%20different%20community%20care%20programs%20into%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVA%20guidelines%20established%20under%20the%20Mission%20Act%20say%20veterans%20can%20seek%20outside%20care%20if%20they%20face%20more%20than%20a%2030-minute%20drive%20for%20primary%20care%20or%20mental%20health%20services%20or%2060%20minutes%20for%20specialty%20care%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20the%20veteran%20described%20in%20Vance's%20scenario%20of%20driving%20two%20and%20half%20hours%20should%20already%20be%20eligible%20for%20community%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mission%20Act%20received%20bipartisan%20support%20when%20it%20passed%20in%202018%2C%20but%20it%20has%20since%20become%20more%20partisan.%20Republicans%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20VA%20under%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20undermined%20the%20law%20by%20limiting%20the%20number%20of%20referrals%20to%20community%20care.%20Congressional%20Republicans%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.military.com%2Fdaily-news%2F2023%2F04%2F27%2F2-lawmakers-trying-expand-access-outside-doctors-vets-despite-va-push-rein-costs.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehave%20introduced%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmillermeeks.house.gov%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2Fmiller-meeks-bost-colleagues-introduce-bill-improve-and-expand-va-care%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebills%20to%20strengthen%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20eligibility%20guidelines%20and%20make%20it%20hard%20for%20the%20VA%20to%20deny%20a%20referral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocrats%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.military.com%2Fdaily-news%2Fopinions%2F2024%2F08%2F12%2Frepublican-project-2025-takes-dead-aim-veterans-health-and-disability-benefits.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Echarge%20that%20the%20GOP%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20ultimately%20aiming%20to%20privatize%20the%20VA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20point%20to%20Project%202025%2C%20a%20conservative%20think%20tank%20blueprint%20for%20a%20future%20Republican%20president%20that%20calls%20for%20retooling%20the%20VA's%20disability%20ratings%20system%20to%20find%20%26quot%3Bcost%20savings%26quot%3B%20and%20says%20the%20next%20administration%20should%20%26quot%3Brapidly%20and%20explicitly%20codify%20VA%20Mission%20Act%20access%20standards%20in%20legislation%20to%20prevent%20the%20VA%20from%20avoiding%20or%20watering%20down%20the%20requirements%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20was%20written%20by%20former%20Trump%20administration%20officials%20and%20others%20with%20ties%20to%20Trump%2C%20though%20Trump%20has%20tried%20to%20distance%20himself%20from%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Vance%20asserted%20that%20expanding%20access%20to%20outside%20doctors%20could%20cut%20costs%2C%20VA%20officials%20have%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.military.com%2Fdaily-news%2F2024%2F04%2F12%2Fdecade-after-scandal-va-health-care-may-be-another-crossroads.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecommunity%20care%20costs%20have%20been%20growing%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20an%20unsustainable%20rate%20since%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Mission%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20podcast%20interview%2C%20Vance%20also%20discussed%20the%20need%20to%20fire%20%26quot%3Bbad%20apples%26quot%3B%20within%20the%20VA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProbably%2090%25%2C%2095%25%20of%20the%20people%20who%20work%20at%20the%20VA%20are%20fantastic%20human%20beings%2C%20but%20then%20you've%20got%2C%20like%2C%20a%20small%20slice%20of%20the%20VA%20that's%20bad%20apples%20that%20make%20it%20really%20hard%20for%20everybody%20else%20to%20do%20their%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20why%20veterans%20spend%20three%20hours%20on%20the%20phone%20trying%20to%20get%20an%20appointment.%20This%20is%20why%20you%20have%20people%20committing%20suicide%20because%20they're%20waiting%2028%20days%20to%20get%20an%20appointment%20with%20a%20doctor.%20Like%2C%20just%20crazy%2C%20crazy%20stuff.%20But%20it's%20a%20small%20sliver%20of%20the%20VA.%20You%20ought%20to%20fire%20those%20people%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20term%2C%20Trump%20also%20signed%20a%20law%20called%20the%20Department%20of%20Veterans%20Affairs%20Accountability%20and%20Whistleblower%20Protection%20Act%20that%20sought%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20the%20VA%20to%20fire%20employees%20accused%20of%20misconduct%20or%20poor%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20law%20faced%20legal%20challenges%20that%20weakened%20its%20effectiveness%20and%20prompted%20the%20Biden%20administration%20to%20stop%20using%20the%20expedited%20firing%20authorities%20granted%20by%20the%20bill.%20Republicans%20in%20Congress%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fveterans.house.gov%2Fuploadedfiles%2Frestore_va_accountability_act_one_pager.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eworking%20to%20revive%20the%20authorities%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-said-he-would-consider-privatizing-some-veteran-healthcare-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726261587000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e4a0ebbf0250c2149361f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-said-he-would-co