onscious%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20Bezos%20was%20indeed%20the%20buyer%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20dispute%20highlights%20the%20significance%20of%20transparency%20in%20high-profile%20real%20estate%20deals.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20Kryss%20is%20suing%20them%20over%20fraud%20allegations%20by%20the%20real%20estate%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWealthy%20individuals%20often%20shield%20their%20identities%20throughout%20the%20process%20of%20purchasing%20a%20home%2C%20from%20the%20initial%20showing%20through%20the%20closing%2C%26quot%3B%20Miami%20real%20estate%20agent%20Danny%20Hertzberg%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Freal-estate%2Fluxury-homes%2Fjeff-bezos-indian-creek-home-lawsuit-3403cdc7%3Fmod%3Dhp_trending_now_article_pos5%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWSJ%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BMany%20billionaires%2C%20when%20they're%20purchasing%20a%20property%2C%20are%20concerned%20that%20when%20the%20seller%20knows%20their%20identity%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20want%20a%20larger%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20of%20last%20year%2C%20Bezos%20announced%20his%20move%20to%20Miami%20from%20Seattle.%20He%20now%20owns%20more%20than%20four%20bayfront%20acres%20on%20Indian%20Creek%20Island%2C%20a%20gated%20community%20sometimes%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20Billionaire%20Bunker.%20The%20island%20has%20drawn%20well-known%20residents%2C%20including%20Tom%20Brady%2C%20Jared%20Kushner%2C%20and%20Ivanka%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726250340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F505ne8r8_jeff-bezos-lauren-sanchez_625x300_28_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-sues-realtors-after-finding-jeff-bezos-bought-his-home-for-a-discounted-price-6560127%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Brazilian%20businessman%2C%20Leo%20Kryss%2C%20has%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20realtor%20Douglas%20Elliman%2C%20alleging%2