ditation%20sessions%2C%20and%20creative%20residencies%20are%20held%20at%20Vinyasa%20Earth%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20Dev%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20a%20dancer%20hailing%20from%20South%20India.%20Speaking%20about%20his%20journey%20at%20Vinyasa%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20lived%20every%20part%20of%20this%20experience.%20Growing%20up%20I%20watched%20my%20%3Cem%3Enani%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmother)%20plaster%20her%20house%20using%20mud%20and%20natural%20materials.%20Building%20Vinyasa%20brought%20back%20a%20lot%20of%20memories%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20almost%20a%20year%20of%20building%2C%20the%20property%20started%20life%20as%20a%20homestay%20in%202022.%20And%20since%20then%2C%20one%20emotion%20has%20trumped%20every%20other.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350883%2Fengineers-who-run-sustainable-homestays-in-india-bir-terraces-forest-side-farm-jungle-hut%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20energy%20inside%20this%20space%20is%20so%20vibrant%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20each%20time%20one%20enters%2C%20they%20feel%20empowered%20to%20dance%2C%20be%20creative%20or%20simply%20be%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sankalp%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20art%20takes%20precedence%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Sankalp%E2%80%99s%20pet%20peeve%20was%20the%20bed%20in%20his%202%20BHK%20apartment%20that%20he%20shared%20with%20eight%20others.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20so%20many%20dreams%2C%20and%20plans.%20But%20there%20was%20never%20space%20for%20anything.%E2%80%9D%20His%202.5%20ft%20mattress%20led%20him%20to%20wake%20up%20with%20back%20aches%20every%20other%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20he%20started%20Vinyasa%20Earth%2C%20he%20designed%20it%20to%20tackle%20the%20pain%20points%20that%20artists%20often%20experience.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20insistent%20that%20the%20stay%20should%20be%20both%2C%20comfortable%20and%20artistic.%20I%20thought%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20dancers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20mattresses%20at%20Vinyasa%20Earth%20come%20recommended%20by%20physiotherapists.%20They%20measure%20four%20feet%20in%20width%20so%20one%20can%20sleep%20well.%20The%20whole%20space%20is%20designed%20with%20a%20certain%20kind%20of%20flow.%20There%20is%20a%20story%20in%20every%20wall%20at%20Vinyasa.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FqndI7Cb9kvw%3Fsi%3DXpjhLA-iD3-09gO0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20draws%20at%20the%20stay%20is%20the%20amphitheatre.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20host%20numerous%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F116831%2Fmale-kathak-dancers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresidencies%20for%20dancers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20theatre%20artists%2C%20and%20filmmakers%20here.%20Teachers%20from%20across%20the%20world%20come%20for%20these%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sankalp%20sharing%20that%20this%20year%20they%20are%20keen%20on%20hosting%20a%20retreat%20for%20elderly%20people%20which%20is%20curated%20keeping%20their%20needs%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20aren%E2%80%99t%20watching%20(or%20taking%20part)%20in%20these%20residencies%2C%20there%20is%20much%20to%20keep%20you%20occupied%20%E2%80%94%20yoga%2C%20forest%20baths%2C%20village%20walks%2C%20meditation%2C%20trekking%2C%20pottery%2C%20sharing%20circles%2C%20%3Cem%3ERajasthani%20%3C%2Fem%3Efolk%20performances%2C%20open%20mics%2C%20star%20gazing%2C%20jam%20sessions%2C%20art%20exhibitions%2C%20and%20sustainable%20building%20workshops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%